                    <cite class="fn"><a href='http://Www.silvergoldnews.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Mr SGN</a></cite>
                    <span class="comment-meta">
                        <a class="rtp-common-link rtp-comment-date" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/10/06/thoughts-on-the-silk-road-raid-trolling-the-fbi-and-the-future-of-bitcoin/#comment-14491" title="October 6, 2013">
                            <time datetime="2013-10-06">October 6, 2013 at 5:43 pm</time>
